{"tid":1403621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學]唯一防鬼方法","createTime":"2019-08-03T20:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T03:58:11.000Z","uid":182088,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"60e2f3fde36c8e149f138fcdb088827737082053","tid":1403621,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:08:50.000Z","msg":"純分析帖文<br />\n示威者不論正面、戰術、陣地、資源都無可能羸差佬<br />\n示威者只係係<span style=\"color: red;\">人數</span>方面佔優同<span style=\"color: red;\">主動性</span>方面佔優：<br />\n1. 示威者人數多過佢<br />\n2. 示威者去邊佢就要佈署去邊/包圍邊到，呢樣野需要時間<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">時間線</span><br />\n就消息所見，其實<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8點左右已經包圍警署</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">7:43分 已經開始圍緊警署</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vaPn0U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vaPn0U.png&h=0022509b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">8:03分 現場一直做完唔同形式既對抗行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/beqr9FU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbeqr9FU.png&h=6b45967b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">9:21分 對方派出大量差佬包圍，尖沙咀、旺角同時用催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOA4aKM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOA4aKM.png&h=e8aaa2b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">9:34 手足被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qPpbWH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qPpbWH.png&h=7a5adee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢段時間入面，足足有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">90分鐘既警察佈防時間</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當大家都知現場有鬼，而<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>鬼係永遠要配合警察行動</strong></span>(不論叫散水、衝、行邊條路都好)<br />\n大家都知，沙田新城市之後，警方永遠會採取大規模、迅速既拘捕行為，鬼亦會配合呢點去做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁點解，我地永遠要係警察佈防完，鬼又開始做野既時候先識考慮走唔走？<br />\n<br />\n唯一防鬼既方法，就係<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">唔好長時間聚集係某位置、唔好太有planning</span></strong>！<br />\n當示威者漫無目的行逛果陣，鬼既影響力係1 (佢只能夠叫人去行去某地方, 相對上易察覺問題)<br />\n當示威者坐低休息、包圍建築物果陣，鬼既影響力就係90 (叫人做乜都言之有理, 衝=要勇武、走=明日再戰、簡路線=安全)<br />\n所以要防鬼，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只能夠係警察包圍、行動之前就防</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能你會覺得咁同元朗7半叫人散水有乜分別<br />\n但現家既目標係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不被捕呀</span></strong></span><br />\n當速龍一衝，根本示威者人多人少係無分別，因為全部人都只會縮！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4i4JRKcFlcI&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4i4JRKcFlcI%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=df418ed5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4i4JRKcFlcI&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果無辦法令其他人有膽留係原地，早散水同遲散水有咩分別</span></span></strong><br />\n(只要目標達到 eg. 紅隧、國旗)？<br />\n<br />\n希望大家認真諗一諗"},{"pid":"99486c0f180d2ae184bc96d02cd6100cac1e66b7","tid":1403621,"uid":182088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:13:23.000Z","msg":"當速龍一衝，係無反抗意識既情況下，人多反而係障礙呀！"},{"pid":"fdffe0288e3c1aaf8af96bf022ce411cca427de8","tid":1403621,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0101af89002b9f42b9ee90fdf697cd3e34ba4f26","tid":1403621,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:58:11.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}